Package com.gridgraph.graphcore.transaction

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    IDataTransaction
    Interface that defines operation on user data to be supported by transaction mechanism
    Note: note that for almost ALL the methods provided by this class, an explicit parameter isn't listed, means the graph object.
    IGridTransaction
    Generic interface for transaction mechanism support by GridGraph
    IMetaDataTransaction
    Interface that defines operation on meta data to be supported by transaction mechanism
    Note: note that for almost ALL the methods provided by this class, an explicit parameter isn't listed, means the graph object.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    EdgeChainIterator
    A EdgeChainIterator is an Iterator, which, by specifying a star vertex, iterates all its edges.
    GraphDataTransaction
    Graph transaction is used to deal with the transactions of graph data.
    GraphDataTransaction.Exceptions
    Common exceptions to use with a GraphDataTransaction.
    GraphMetaDataTransaction
    Graph transaction is used to deal with the transactions of graph meta data.
    GraphMetaDataTransaction.Exceptions
    Common exceptions to use with a GraphMetaDataTransaction.
    GridGraphTransaction
    A ThreadLocal transaction for graph operations.
    IGridTransaction.Exceptions
    Common exceptions to use with a IGridTransaction.
    PipelineData
    Get graph data from storage in the form of pipeline
